Title: The NSA is Watching You: The Government, Surveillance, and You
Presenters: Eva Galperin, Cory Doctorow, Nick Farr
Book Description: 'Now that Edward Snowden has made you aware that the government is watching and recording your every move- come join our GoH Eva Galperin and Featured Guests Cory Doctorow and Nick Farr as they discuss of the implications of living in a surveillance state. '

Title: Bitcoin, Dogecoin, and Cryptocurrencies… What’s the Big Deal?
Book Description: 'What's a cryptocurrency and why do we need it? What is Bitcoin mining? Why is Bitcoin so volatile? What is this scary new money and why is it important in our ever-changing world?'

Title: Your Personal Penguicon with a Passport!
Book Description: 'It's finally time: You need to visit Germany and Japan! Whatever your interest is- odds are you'll find a unique spin on it overseas that will change your life and how you view humanity. With nearly half a million transcontinental miles flown east and west- Nick Farr will regale you with tales of the geekiest highlights in both countries and tips on how to have an authentic- safe- geeky and budget-conscious international trip to Germany and Japan.'
